Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你要取消？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.95,0:01:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你在阿富汗的失態\n我們也有聽聞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你是想說我把事情搞砸了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,像你這種會把\n重要商品丟下逃走的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我們無法信任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,信任是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的，多虧那小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:02:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,害我連打工都打不成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多也該回歸本業了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,#18 深海派對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如你所見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這是文化祭的入口門
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,一點都看不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,給我說明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽說去年的主題是“和平”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,因此，今年的主題是“保安”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這道門可兼為維護治安的\n觀測與防衛據點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,就算全副武裝的恐怖份子\n前來襲擊文化祭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這道門的設計\n能撐住相當長的一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,上次出差回來以後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你的戰爭癡呆\n是不是越來越嚴重了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,還有你們也都不覺得奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我們只是贊同相良所說的\n“讓來參加文化祭的人能感到安心”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,看到這種東西會感到安心的\n只有宗介好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，也許我們是有點和平癡呆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但是這個\n“入場歡迎門製作費147萬1000元”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,未免也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,喔，你發現這部分了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我應該可以用超低價買到\n以色列制的複合裝甲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,平常至少也要花500萬…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹嘛突然打我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,文化祭全部的預算是150萬耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果照你所說的去做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,學校什麼活動都辦不成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一能看到的就是\n聳立在正門的這個陰森森的要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,總之，我是不會同意這東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,要是現在不立刻撤走的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,到底發生什麼事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,標識裝置被誤觸啟動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:03:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你這個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你這個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那個顏料對人體無害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是在說這個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在感到悲哀啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不會再有第二次的實貴青春歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然得跟這種完全不體貼的\n戰爭癡呆男吵吵鬧鬧的渡過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,高二的夏天\n對女孩子來說可是特別的季節耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可是，已經無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在開學前的這一個禮拜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我會在家裡\n安安靜靜地混吃等死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說你這禮拜很閑是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,對啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真不好意思喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要跟我一起去南方島嶼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我們兩人去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你是認真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,之前就想邀你去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我來慰勞你們囉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,現在氣氛正好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,還是算了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你不會做奇怪的事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會做奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不危險嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,也不危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可…可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你這麼堅持的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要我陪你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥，你還好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？不要緊，不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,果然夏天還是適合藍色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好像太大膽了點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,帶這件去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,反正你大概也只有\n學校泳裝之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這件也帶去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,單獨兩人去會不會不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,算了，反正對方是宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,想做錯事都不太可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,(把夏天的回憶保存起來喔 BY恭子)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到相良會這麼大膽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就當作是夏末的一次小小冒險吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,識別不明艦，持續保持衝撞路線
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,潛…潛航後依然持續接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡，為什麼不躲開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,對方應該也發現了才對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,距離100
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,距離50
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,距離30
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,20
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,全員隨便找個東西抓緊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,消…消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,消失得無影無蹤…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:06:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能會有那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,檢查BQQ-5，快去\N說不定這就是傳聞中的“TOY BOX”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是關於幽靈潛水艇的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,體積非常的大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不聲不響的出現
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不聲不響的消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,而且速度快得驚人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,如果剛才遇到的是\N那艘“TOY BOX”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那艘船的艦長\n一定是個性格扭曲的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,下三爛的瘋狂傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這份大禮我一定會還你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,您怎麼了？艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,做了有點對不起“巴薩狄那”的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,希望他不要太沮喪才好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我的話\n自尊心一定會大大受創吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,又沒有演習的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有成果了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:08:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,將一般前進時的靜音性\n再往下方修正一點或許比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼，我們回基地去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不然會趕不上生日宴會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,而且，明天島上有客人要來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,要坐這個去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這是為了你而準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀，我真的對你刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到你準備得這麼周到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼，我們要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,去秘銀西太平洋部隊基地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,泰斯塔羅莎上校想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,線路E2傳來任務訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,收訊完成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,馬德加斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,回基地要暫緩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,宴會也要中止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣往南方前進
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.64,0:08:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,目的地的海域是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,昂柳群島是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,跟化學武器有關
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,狀況是儲藏設施\n被某武裝集團襲擊佔領
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真叫人感到可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,要是那座化學武器儲藏庫\n遭到爆破的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼事情就會很嚴重了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那個小國可能會遭到毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,美軍應該會派\n裝備AS的特殊部隊過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,要是這樣能解決就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,請問有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,相良宗介士官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有什麼不滿的話\n希望你能說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我會盡可能的加以改善
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,喔，如果是這件事的話\n反正你是不可能解決得了的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我就不說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,相良士官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,美麗達島傳來通訊了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:09:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,B待機？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他們說要你儘快趕來\n航行中的De Danann
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,小要也要一起過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥也？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,她可是平民耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這是泰莎的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,換個方向想想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,De Danann可說是\n世上最安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就帶她一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你有帶泳裝嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,基本上是有帶啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,把它換上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以去客艙的後方換
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,換完後\n把手提行李放進這個袋子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,全都放進去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼突然…等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,快點，沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你那身打扮…該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你穿上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快點…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我幫你穿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,做什麼啦\n士官，還有一分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:10:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,沒時間了，無法重來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道，不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，到底要做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,還有30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,後會有期
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,後會有期？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧，千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你該不會想從這裡跳下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,蔚藍的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,蔚藍的大海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,單獨兩人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,確認著水了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,著水後的人在水面胡亂掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是溺水了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,聽到激烈的打水聲與尖叫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,情況不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,請把聲音傳到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,住手，千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,少囉唆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:12:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你有絲毫考慮到我的心情嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我最討厭你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,沉下去吧，你這個呆頭鵝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不用管他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨Tuatha De Danann
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像很累了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,從飛機上被推下來，被丟到海裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,然後再咕嚕咕嚕的潛到水裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,除了某個士官大人之外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一般人都會累的，真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,本來想請你到美麗達島基地的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,因為狀況有點改變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我也想見泰莎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你也有很多事想談吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:13:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，那也是原因之一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,相良士官
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是，上校大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,請你去主機庫一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不管跟誰都好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,幫我跟他說一聲\n“我等一下就過去”好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,小要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能請你先換回便服？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在帶你去參觀艦內
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡很窄對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不過在潛艦中\n這樣算是很寬的通路了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,同時也考慮到緊急時\n必須奔跑的乘員安全
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧這種設計
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,讓這裡少了很多\n因為撞到東西而跌倒的蠢蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，你還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這點小事不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真是叫人看得冒冷汗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的是艦長嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,被你這麼說，我實在有點羞愧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但是這艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我家一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有我不知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,當然不包括乘員的隱私
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼，請往這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然小要你可能\n不太喜歡這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,立正
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,向當泰斯塔羅莎上校與部隊\n瀕臨種種危機時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,展現其勇氣、行動力\n以及深厚人情的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥要小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,致上最高的謝意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,敬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,知道小要你要來以後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,大家說無論如何都想表示敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,感到很光榮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我沒有做那麼偉大的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:14:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你所做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,即使是獨當一面的士兵\n都無法輕易做到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,請你感到自傲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,馬德加斯中校說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,小要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼歡迎儀式就到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來會在這裡\n舉辦一場小型派對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,請小要也要一起參加喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,派對？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是這孩子的一歲生日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,來喔，來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,終於到了艦內賓果大會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,榮耀的頭獎開獎時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這是個很棒的獎品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,說實話，我很想要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這個獎品就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,泰斯塔羅莎艦長的熱吻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,威巴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我可沒聽說有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,“有什麼我能幫忙的請儘管說喔”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你明明這麼說了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我確實是有說過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不要的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,換成提供\n“愛用內衣”之類的也可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那我更不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那就熱吻囉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,艦長也說OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,O的65
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,已經是第五次了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,有聽牌的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多該有了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,幸…幸福的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好，重新振作精神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續下一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會…竟然要接吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:16:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,N的42
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,聽牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我這邊也聽牌了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,場面越來越熱鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,勝利的女神究竟會對誰微笑呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,宗介嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,馬卡蘭嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,亦或是梁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,相良…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,請你一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,B的13
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起了，各位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,賓果啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,頭獎得主竟然是馬卡蘭上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,艦長，熱情一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉，跟我熱吻不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼，上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,當然，艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我深感光榮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,今天真是我這輩子\n最棒的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我真走運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是ECHO-84，被擊中了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,求救！求救！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,腳被擊中了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,誰來支援一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡，那個紅色的傢伙\n竟然把波布給…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,誰來救救我，救…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能會有這種蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,沒子彈了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,景氣真差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,順便告訴你，你是最後一個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才雖然也有個\n哭著求饒的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,真是辛苦了，阿兵哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,別開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我來示範給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,果然真的很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,身材又好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,品味也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她身邊的男人\n當然不會放過她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,既然這樣，那你為什麼要歎氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是擔心他們鬧得太凶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這艘潛艦可是在執行作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然還演奏音樂…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼脫節的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是泰莎說可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,身為小兵的你沒資格\n說什麼有的沒的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,話是沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都會感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不管經歷過多少次的戰役
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，星條旗永遠飄揚是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那群傢伙似乎到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,喔？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有情報傳來\n他們在海上與突襲部隊會合了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真是群有禮貌的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,緊緊的咬住我們的魚餌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,0:20:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,還有之前的那兩人\n可能也一起坐上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,喔，那對情侶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那不錯，太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他們跟秘銀的傢伙們\n一起死掉的話不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會讓那女的死的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,意外事故總是會發生的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.45,0:22:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在艦內的浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,全裸的毛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.83,0:22:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,對全裸的小要與泰莎所吐露出的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.00,0:22:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,赤裸裸的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,火熱熱的全裸肌膚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,把本大爺的活躍緊緊的…
